# NOTICE

EdgeFirst Hardware Abstraction Layer (HAL)  
Copyright 2025 Au-Zone Technologies

This product includes software developed at Au-Zone Technologies (https://au-zone.com/).

## Third-Party Software

See THIRD_PARTY.md in releases for complete attribution of third-party dependencies.

This project uses the following major open-source components:

- Rust Standard Library and toolchain
- PyO3 - Python bindings for Rust
- ndarray - N-dimensional array library
- rayon - Data parallelism library
- fast_image_resize - Image resizing library
- zune-jpeg, zune-png - Image decoding libraries
- dma-heap - Linux DMA heap allocator
- four-char-code - FourCC format utilities

For a complete list of dependencies with their licenses, run:
```bash
cargo tree --prefix none --edges normal | sort -u
```

All dependencies are compatible with the Apache License 2.0.
